{"TopicId":208192,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Painting headshields.","CreatedByName":"Jeq","CreatedById":172375,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-15T09:50:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jeq","CreatedById":172375,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-15T09:50:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKsp1 was limited for its heatshields for only round parts. It could be better if we could use paint tool to generate heat shield on any wanted surface.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Defenestrator47","CreatedById":145983,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-15T22:55:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed.\u00A0 Even better if that could have a gameplay effect - painted surface has heatshield properties, but with associated costs as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ryaja","CreatedById":221431,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T21:58:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, although it could be a little overpowered, you just cover your whole craft in a heatsheild and no heat damage.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joseph Kerman","CreatedById":176176,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-23T03:05:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224135747\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208192\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653170290\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221431\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ryaja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/22/2022 at 5:58 AM, Ryaja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, although it could be a little overpowered, you just cover your whole craft in a heatsheild and no heat damage.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMass cost?\u00A0 Lower fuel fraction? Perhaps it could also be not a lot, which means you probably aren\u0027t doing repeated re-entries without risk of overheat.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cs\u003EAnd that\u0027s assuming you\u0027re going fast enough for heating to be a massive problem\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ryaja","CreatedById":221431,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-23T03:37:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe only certain spots on a part would work like the bottom and nose of a space plane\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Catto","CreatedById":137773,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-23T14:12:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224136211\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208192\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653277056\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221431\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ryaja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Ryaja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe only certain spots on a part would work like the bottom and nose of a space plane\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. We need that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-23T20:03:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224136211\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208192\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653277056\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221431\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ryaja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, Ryaja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ne the bottom and nose of a space plane\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, also if they add larger \u0022starship style\u0022 parts, I would love the ability to add heat shields on that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ryaja","CreatedById":221431,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-23T20:47:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYa\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}